them with one of their fingers.
               The 9. note of Antichriſt. All their workes do they
for the intent that they may be ſeene of men.
            Alſo they goe in long religious apparell, they muſt be
had in reuerence, and ſaluted with names and titles of dignity,
they ſhut vp the kingdome of heauen before men,The 10. note of Antichriſt. both
