nor denie it before men. Which trueth ſaith He that
denieth me before men,Luke 12. ſhal be denied before the Angels
of God.Mat. 10. 
               Alſo, He that endureth to the end, ſhal be
ſaued. Therefore, ſo manie as pertaine vnto faith, muſt
holde faith, ſlicke vnto Chriſt, ſtand faſt, and walke in the
